aws cloudformation deploy \
  --template-file template.yaml \
  --stack-name iam-guardian \
  --capabilities CAPABILITY_NAMED_IAM

---CloudFormation will:---

Create an IAM Role with permissions for Access Analyzer and IAM operations.

Create a Lambda Function using your lambda_function.py file.

Create an EventBridge Rule (IAMGuardianScheduleRule) that automatically triggers the Lambda every 24 hours.

Create the necessary Lambda permissions so EventBridge can invoke it.
